  <h1 class="page-title">Installation</h1>
  <p class="page-lead">Get Atmos running locally in minutes. You'll need <a href="https://nodejs.org" target="_blank">Node.js 18+</a> and <a href="https://git-scm.com" target="_blank">Git</a> installed on your machine.</p>

